知想點"},{"pid":"8ae72d011859f3d1e3f251a204f015c4c295e68d","tid":14750,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:51:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日玩住手機 好似無左自己咁 點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇書，認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c13dc30fc14c164e740504e4060437f84050d8","tid":14750,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31592a314dfe742278a7ad123e1907de33d9856","tid":14750,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:55:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成日玩住手機 好似無左自己咁 點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇書，認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇完書 再叫雞"},{"pid":"d308f31ffa92c5102bfb486345be90b6a7bf21d7","tid":14750,"uid":15960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:55:36.000Z","msg":"I help you"},{"pid":"4a27429d28643e83159ea473f7b76c33fdc7a7c6","tid":14750,"uid":41859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:56:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成日玩住手機 好似無左自己咁 點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇書，認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇完書 再叫雞</blockquote><br />\n花店條女 好大波"},{"pid":"f1aba2d59de890a4102fc610b6443273baec194c","tid":14750,"uid":41859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:57:18.000Z","msg":"呢個post唔吹水啊 比意見我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b94333bff3b6d64c00d5661af1aee81578a50e","tid":14750,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:57:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><b